    "cultural_notes": "While bean sprouts are used in various cuisines worldwide, this stir-fry is a modern Ugandan take that incorporates local flavors and ingredients. It represents a growing interest in fresh, plant-based, and quick-cooking meals, especially in urban areas. It's a great way to enjoy the nutritional benefits of sprouts in a familiar, flavorful format."
